{\rtf1\ansi \deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss .VnArial;}}{\colortbl;\red0\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;\red128\green0\blue64;\red0\green0\blue255;}\deftab1134\plain \f0 \fs24 \pard\qj \sl240 \tx1134 \tx2268 \tx3402 \tx4536 \tx5670 \tx6804 \tx7938 \tx9072 \tx10206 \tx11340 \tx12474 \tx13608 \tx14742 \tx4 \tab M\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng v\'f2 kh\'dd c\'e6 x\'ada v\'b5 \'ae\'e9c \'ae\'b8o nh\'cat do con ng\'ad\'eai ch\'d5 t\'b9o ra ch\'ddnh l\'b5 "boumerang". T\'aan g\'e4i c\'f1a v\'f2 kh\'dd n\'b5y l\'b5 ti\'d5ng c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'e9 l\'b9c th\'e6 d\'a9n sinh s\'e8ng \'eb v\'efng \'ae\'cat n\'bbm trong bang New South Wales (\'f3c).\par \tab V\'f2 kh\'dd th\'ab s\'ac n\'b5y \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t b\'e9 l\'b9c c\'dfn trong t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng s\'ac khai ch\'d5 t\'b9o ra t\'f5 khi n\'b5o th\'d7 kh\'abng ai bi\'d5t nh\'adng n\'e3 \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho c\'b8c nh\'b5 khoa h\'e4c b\'e8i r\'e8i kh\'abng \'ddt. Kh\'abng ai c\'e3 th\'d3 gi\'b6i th\'ddch tho\'b6 \'ae\'b8ng t\'b9i sao khi li\'d6ng n\'e3 \'aei, n\'e3 bay trong kh\'abng kh\'dd r\'e5i l\'b9i t\'f9 n\'e3 c\'e3 th\'d3 quay v\'dfng tr\'eb l\'b9i ch\'e7 ng\'ad\'eai n\'d0m. M\'c6t kh\'b8c, v\'f2 kh\'dd n\'b5y \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'cay s\'f6 d\'f4ng \'eb ba \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng v\'b5o th\'eai \'ae\'b9i m\'b5 h\'b5ng h\'b6i l\'b5 ph\'ad\'acng ti\'d6n duy nh\'cat \'ae\'d3 giao th\'abng gi\'f7a c\'b8c ch\'a9u l\'f4c n\'aan c\'f2ng kh\'e3 n\'e3i c\'b8c b\'e9 l\'b9c "d\'b9y" nhau. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 m\'e9t b\'e9 l\'b9c \'eb \'f3c, m\'e9t \'eb \'a7\'abng B\'bec Phi Ch\'a9u, m\'e9t \'eb mi\'d2n nam \'can \'a7\'e9 v\'b5 b\'e9 l\'b9c da \'ae\'e1 \'eb bang Arizona (Hoa K\'fa). Tuy nhi\'aan, n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n Boumerang ng\'ad\'eai ta th\'ad\'eang ngh\'dc \'ae\'d5n th\'f8 v\'f2 kh\'dd c\'f1a th\'e6 d\'a9n \'f3c ch\'a9u.\par \tab C\'e3 hai lo\'b9i Boumerang : lo\'b9i "\'aei lu\'abn" v\'b5 lo\'b9i "quay l\'b9i". Tuy nhi\'aan, kh\'b6 n\'a8ng s\'b8t th\'ad\'acng c\'f1a lo\'b9i "\'aei lu\'abn" cao h\'acn c\'f1a lo\'b9i "quay l\'b9i". Ng\'ad\'eai ta n\'e3i r\'bbng v\'edi c\'b8i boumerang lo\'b9i "\'aei lu\'abn", m\'e9t th\'e6 d\'a9n ch\'a9u \'f3c c\'e3 th\'d3 ch\'c6t \'ae\'abi m\'e9t con v\'cbt nh\'e1 \'aeang ch\'b9y. Tuy nhi\'aan, lo\'b9i "quay l\'b9i" n\'e6i ti\'d5ng h\'acn v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'c7u nh\'ad c\'b6 th\'d5 gi\'edi bi\'d5t \'ae\'d5n v\'d2 s\'f9 l\'b9 l\'efng c\'f1a n\'e3. Th\'cbt ra, th\'e6 d\'a9n ch\'a9u \'f3c ch\'d8 coi boumerang l\'b5 m\'e9t th\'f8 \'ae\'e5 ch\'aci ch\'f8 kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 m\'e9t v\'f2 kh\'dd quan tr\'e4ng. \'a7\'abi khi n\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'efng \'ae\'d3 "ch\'d0m" chim ch\'e3c.\par \tab Boumerang \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b5m b\'bbng g\'e7 c\'e3 hai c\'b8nh h\'aci d\'d1p g\'c7n gi\'e8ng nh\'ad hai c\'b8nh cung v\'edi m\'e9t g\'e3c kho\'b6ng t\'f5 90 \'ae\'d5n 120 \'ae\'e9. Hai c\'b8nh cung c\'e3 m\'e9t m\'d0p d\'b5y, m\'e9t m\'d0p m\'e1ng v\'b5 h\'aci v\'aanh v\'edi nhau kho\'b6ng 2 \'ae\'e9 so v\'edi m\'c6t ph\'bcng ngang c\'bet trung t\'a9m c\'f1a boumerang. Kh\'abng kh\'dd \'d0p l\'aan ch\'e7 ph\'d7nh ra c\'f1a ph\'dda m\'d0p d\'b5y v\'b5 \'ae\'e9 v\'aanh h\'ad\'edng xu\'e8ng \'ae\'b7 khi\'d5n cho boumerang bay v\'dfng tr\'eb l\'b9i.   \par \tab Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai s\'ac khai \'eb \'f3c ch\'a9u \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 th\'d3 ch\'d5 t\'b9o boumerang cong m\'e9t c\'b8ch l\'b9 l\'efng. H\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'d0m n\'e3 bay \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t qu\'b7ng \'ae\'ad\'eang th\'bcng d\'b5i g\'c7n 30m theo m\'e9t \'ae\'ad\'eang v\'dfng \'ae\'ad\'eang k\'ddnh kho\'b6ng 25m r\'e5i quay tr\'eb l\'b9i ng\'ad\'eai n\'d0m ho\'c6c h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'d0m cho boumerang ch\'b9m \'ae\'cat r\'e5i v\'dfng l\'aan v\'b5 quay tr\'eb l\'b9i ng\'ad\'eai n\'d0m. Khi n\'d0m boumerang v\'d2 ph\'dda tr\'ad\'edc, c\'e6 tay ph\'b6i v\'c6n quay xu\'e8ng ph\'dda d\'ad\'edi. Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 th\'cay c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai n\'d0m \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t c\'b8i boumerang bay xa g\'c7n 40m r\'e5i m\'edi bay v\'dfng tr\'eb l\'b9i.\par \pard\qr \sl240 \tx1134 \tx2268 \tx3402 \tx4536 \tx5670 \tx6804 \tx7938 \tx9072 \tx10206 \tx11340 \tx12474 \tx13608 \tx14742 \tx4 \par \plain \f0 \fs18 Tr\'ddch t\'f5 \plain \f0 \fs18 \i \cf3 H\'b7y tr\'b6 l\'eai em t\'b9i sao\plain \f0 \fs18 \i \par \plain \f0 \fs18 \b \cf4 (ARKADY LEOKUM)\plain \f0 \fs24 \par \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab }